metadata.name: Unforgotten Objects V2
metadata.description:
We’re in the 2022, alot of new game machines and consoles have been made, but there’s always something that reminding us of our beautiful past days, “Gameboy” is one of the biggest past days reminder of our lifes, an “Object” made our days fun with full of gold and diamond moments. Your shapes are always in our minds, you’re never forgotten.

V2
